[[example]]
name = "cursor"
required-features = [ "image", "png",]

[[example]]
name = "image"
required-features = [ "image", "png",]

[[example]]
name = "invalidation"
required-features = [ "im",]

[[example]]
name = "list"
required-features = [ "im",]

[[example]]
name = "svg"
required-features = [ "svg",]

[[example]]
name = "tabs"
required-features = [ "im",]

[[example]]
name = "widget_gallery"
required-features = [ "svg", "im", "image", "png",]

[package]
name = "druid"
version = "0.7.0"
license = "Apache-2.0"
authors = [ "Raph Levien <raph.levien@gmail.com>",]
description = "Data-oriented Rust UI design toolkit."
repository = "https://github.com/linebender/druid"
categories = [ "gui",]
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "toolkit",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
default = [ "gtk",]
gtk = [ "druid-shell/gtk",]
image = [ "druid-shell/image",]
svg = [ "usvg",]
x11 = [ "druid-shell/x11",]
wayland = [ "druid-shell/wayland",]
crochet = []
serde = [ "im/serde", "druid-shell/serde",]
raw-win-handle = [ "druid-shell/raw-win-handle",]
png = [ "druid-shell/image_png",]
jpeg = [ "druid-shell/jpeg",]
jpeg_rayon = [ "druid-shell/jpeg_rayon",]
gif = [ "druid-shell/gif",]
bmp = [ "druid-shell/bmp",]
ico = [ "druid-shell/ico",]
tiff = [ "druid-shell/tiff",]
webp = [ "druid-shell/webp",]
pnm = [ "druid-shell/pnm",]
dds = [ "druid-shell/dds",]
tga = [ "druid-shell/tga",]
farbfeld = [ "druid-shell/farbfeld",]
dxt = [ "druid-shell/dxt",]
hdr = [ "druid-shell/hdr",]
image-all = [ "image", "svg", "png", "jpeg", "jpeg_rayon", "gif", "bmp", "ico", "tiff", "webp", "pnm", "dds", "tga", "farbfeld", "dxt", "hdr",]

[dependencies]
fluent-bundle = "0.15.1"
fluent-langneg = "0.13.0"
fluent-syntax = "0.11.0"
unic-langid = "0.9.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.6.0"
xi-unicode = "0.3.0"
fnv = "1.0.7"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "=3.1.0"

[dependencies.druid-shell]
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false
path = "../druid-shell"

[dependencies.druid-derive]
version = "0.4.0"
path = "../druid-derive"

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.22"

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.2"
features = [ "fmt", "ansi",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.instant]
version = "0.1.6"
features = [ "wasm-bindgen",]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.19"
optional = true

[dependencies.im]
version = "15.0.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.usvg]
version = "0.14.1"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.float-cmp]
version = "0.8.0"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.piet-common]
version = "=0.5.0"
features = [ "png",]

[dev-dependencies.pulldown-cmark]
version = "0.8"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.test-log]
version = "0.2.5"
features = [ "trace",]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.2"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch=\"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies]
open = "1.6"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "im",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
default-target = "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc"
cargo-args = [ "-Zunstable-options", "-Zrustdoc-scrape-examples=examples",]

[target."cfg(target_arch=\"wasm32\")".dependencies.tracing-wasm]
version = "0.2.0"

[target."cfg(target_arch=\"wasm32\")".dependencies.console_error_panic_hook]
version = "0.1.6"

[package]
name = "druid-derive"
version = "0.4.0"
license = "Apache-2.0"
authors = [ "Druid authors",]
description = "derive impls for druid, a Rust UI toolkit."
repository = "https://github.com/linebender/druid"
edition = "2018"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
syn = "1.0.39"
quote = "1.0.7"
proc-macro2 = "1.0.19"

[dev-dependencies]
trybuild = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies.druid]
version = "0.7.0"
path = "../druid"

[dev-dependencies.float-cmp]
version = "0.8.0"
features = [ "std",]
default-features = false

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
default-target = "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc"

[package]
name = "druid-shell"
version = "0.7.0"
license = "Apache-2.0"
authors = [ "Raph Levien <raph.levien@gmail.com>",]
description = "Platform abstracting application shell used for druid toolkit."
repository = "https://github.com/linebender/druid"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "os::macos-apis", "os::windows-apis", "gui",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
default = [ "gtk",]
gtk = [ "gdk-sys", "glib-sys", "gtk-sys", "gtk-rs",]
x11 = [ "ashpd", "bindgen", "cairo-sys-rs", "futures", "nix", "pkg-config", "x11rb",]
wayland = [ "wayland-client", "wayland-protocols/client", "wayland-protocols/unstable_protocols", "nix", "cairo-sys-rs", "rand", "calloop", "wayland-cursor", "log", "im", "bindgen", "pkg-config",]
raw-win-handle = [ "raw-window-handle",]
image_png = [ "piet-common/image_png",]
jpeg = [ "piet-common/jpeg",]
jpeg_rayon = [ "piet-common/jpeg_rayon",]
gif = [ "piet-common/gif",]
bmp = [ "piet-common/bmp",]
ico = [ "piet-common/ico",]
tiff = [ "piet-common/tiff",]
webp = [ "piet-common/webp",]
pnm = [ "piet-common/pnm",]
dds = [ "piet-common/dds",]
tga = [ "piet-common/tga",]
farbfeld = [ "piet-common/farbfeld",]
dxt = [ "piet-common/dxt",]
hdr = [ "piet-common/hdr",]
serde = [ "kurbo/serde",]

[dependencies]
piet-common = "=0.5.0"
kurbo = "0.8.2"
tracing = "0.1.22"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
time = "0.3.0"
cfg-if = "1.0.0"
anyhow = "1.0.32"

[dev-dependencies]
static_assertions = "1.1.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.7.0"

[dependencies.instant]
version = "0.1.6"
features = [ "wasm-bindgen",]

[dependencies.keyboard-types]
version = "0.6.2"
default_features = false

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.23.12"
optional = true
default_features = false

[dependencies.raw-window-handle]
version = "0.4.2"
optional = true
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.piet-common]
version = "=0.5.0"
features = [ "png",]

[dev-dependencies.test-log]
version = "0.2.5"
features = [ "trace",]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.2"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.58"
optional = true

[build-dependencies.pkg-config]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os=\"windows\")".dependencies]
scopeguard = "1.1.0"
wio = "0.2.2"

[target."cfg(target_os=\"macos\")".dependencies]
block = "0.1.6"
cocoa = "0.24.0"
objc = "0.2.7"
core-graphics = "0.22.0"
foreign-types = "0.3.2"
bitflags = "1.2.1"

[target."cfg(target_arch=\"wasm32\")".dependencies]
wasm-bindgen = "0.2.67"
js-sys = "0.3.44"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
default-target = "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc"

[target."cfg(target_os=\"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3.9"
features = [ "d2d1_1", "dwrite", "winbase", "libloaderapi", "errhandlingapi", "winuser", "shellscalingapi", "shobjidl", "combaseapi", "synchapi", "dxgi1_3", "dcomp", "d3d11", "dwmapi", "wincon", "fileapi", "processenv", "winbase", "handleapi", "shellapi", "winnls",]

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.ashpd]
version = "0.3.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.cairo-rs]
version = "0.14.0"
default_features = false
features = [ "xcb",]

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.cairo-sys-rs]
version = "0.14.0"
default_features = false
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.21"
optional = true
features = [ "executor",]

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.gdk-sys]
version = "0.14.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.gtk-rs]
version = "0.14.0"
features = [ "v3_22",]
package = "gtk"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.glib-sys]
version = "0.14.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.gtk-sys]
version = "0.14.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.nix]
version = "0.18.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.x11rb]
version = "0.8.0"
features = [ "allow-unsafe-code", "present", "render", "randr", "xfixes", "xkb", "resource_manager", "cursor",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.wayland-client]
version = "0.29"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.29"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.wayland-cursor]
version = "0.29"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.rand]
version = "0.8.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.calloop]
version = "0.7.1"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.log]
version = "0.4.14"
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os=\"linux\", target_os=\"openbsd\"))".dependencies.im]
version = "15.0.0"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_arch=\"wasm32\")".dependencies.web-sys]
version = "0.3.44"
features = [ "Window", "MouseEvent", "CssStyleDeclaration", "WheelEvent", "KeyEvent", "KeyboardEvent", "Navigator",]
